dataset.name: xly_ctm_buy
dataset.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) ctmSum,SUM(cb.`MYS_Q`) MYS_Q, SUM(cb.`MYS_J`) MYS_J, SUM(cb.`MYS_C`) MYS_C, SUM(cb.`MYS_D`) MYS_D, SUM(cb.`BDMY_Q`) BDMY_Q, SUM(cb.`BDMY_J`) BDMY_J, SUM(cb.`BDMY_D`) BDMY_D, SUM(cb.`XSY_Q`) XSY_Q, SUM(cb.`XSY_J`) XSY_J, SUM(cb.`XSY_D`) XSY_D, SUM(cb.`MF_C`) MF_C, SUM(cb.`MF_D`) MF_D, cb.`SALE_MGR_ID` ,cb.`SALE_MGR_NAME`,cb.`END_MONTH` FROM xly_ctm_buy cb WHERE cb.`END_MONTH`=:endMonth GROUP BY cb.`SALE_MGR_ID`
